sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  actor U as User
  participant FE as React Frontend
  participant BE as FastAPI Backend
  participant RAG as RAG Engine
  participant MR as Model Router
  participant LLM as Selected LLM
  U->>FE: Upload CSV or Excel file
  FE->>BE: POST /upload (multipart)
  BE->>BE: Validate size, MIME, encoding
  BE->>BE: Detect format (CSV vs Excel)
  BE->>RAG: Parse file with Pandas / openpyxl
  RAG->>RAG: Build schema, stats, chunks
  RAG->>RAG: Embed chunks (Gemini) into FAISS
  RAG-->>BE: session_id + profile + detected_format
  BE-->>FE: 200 OK upload response
  FE-->>U: Render dashboard + chat panel
  U->>FE: Ask question + pick model
  FE->>BE: POST /chat {session_id, query, model_id}
  BE->>RAG: Retrieve relevant context
  RAG-->>BE: Context chunks + schema
  BE->>MR: Build prompt and route(model_id)
  MR->>LLM: Send grounded prompt
  LLM-->>MR: Generated answer
  MR-->>BE: Answer text
  BE-->>FE: Response + context_used
  FE-->>U: Render answer with source rows
